---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>🧑‍🚀 Hey, Techies !</h1>
			<p>Welcome to my corner of the internet — your new go-to space for everything <strong>software engineering</strong> and <strong>career growth</strong>.</p>
			
			<p>I’m <strong>Shreyash Chavhan</strong>, an SDE-2 at a leading product-based tech company. With over 3 years of hands-on experience in building scalable backend systems, mentoring developers, and solving complex engineering challenges, I’ve built this platform to share everything I’ve learned (and still learning!) in the world of tech.</p>

			<h2>Here’s what you’ll find here:</h2>
			<ul>
			<li><span class="emoji">🚀</span><strong>In-Depth Tech Blogs</strong> — covering system design, backend architecture, cloud, DevOps, and real-world engineering problems.</li>
			<li><span class="emoji">🎯</span><strong>Interview Prep Guides</strong> — practical tips, coding strategies, and mock interview insights for cracking top tech roles.</li>
			<li><span class="emoji">📚</span><strong>Courses & Resources</strong> — curated learning paths and mini-courses for self-paced skill building.</li>
			<li><span class="emoji">🌐</span><strong>Memberships</strong> — access exclusive content, hands-on projects, and community sessions.</li>
			</ul>

			<p>This site isn’t just a blog — it’s a growing <strong>knowledge hub for software developers</strong> aiming to level up their careers.</p>
			
			<p>Let’s build, learn, and grow — together. 🔧💡</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
